<h3 style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: x-large;">Personal Recommendations</span></h3><br /><div style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;">If 13 books are too many to chose from, then check out the following <b>Short List</b>. The five highest rated books on Goodreads (of the 13 listed here) are as follows:</span></div><div><ul style="text-align: left;"><li><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18176747-the-hard-thing-about-hard-things" target="_blank"><b>The Hard Thing About Hard Things</b></a> (4.24 rating out of 5.00)</span></li><li><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18077903-creativity-inc" target="_blank"><b>Creativity, Inc.</b></a> (4.21)</span></li><li><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18050143-zero-to-one" target="_blank"><b>Zero to One</b></a> (4.17)</span></li><li><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/20604826-flash-boys" target="_blank"><b>Flash Boys</b></a> (4.14)</span></li><li><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/16144853-leaders-eat-last" target="_blank"><b>Leaders Eat Last</b></a> (4.14)</span></li></ul></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;">These five books are now on my <b>Short List</b>.</span></div><div><br /></div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;">
