I have read eight books from this list of 13. As I work through this reading list, I will post my reviews at Goodreads.com and share links here.</span><div><ul style="text-align: left;"><li><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1101991700" target="_blank"><b>Creativity, Inc.</b></a>&nbsp;</span><b>★★★★★</b></li><li><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1165331856" target="_blank"><b>Essentialism</b></a>&nbsp;</span><b>★★★★★</b></li><li><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/906922600" target="_blank"><b>Flash Boys</b></a>&nbsp;</span><b>★★★★</b></li><li><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1126998011" target="_blank"><b>How Google Works</b></a>&nbsp;</span><b>★★★★★</b></li><li><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/878591828" target="_blank"><b>Leaders Eat Last</b></a>&nbsp;</span><b>★★★★★</b></li><li><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1165330603" target="_blank"><b>The Second Machine Age</b></a>&nbsp;</span><b>★★★★</b></li><li><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1071129513" target="_blank"><b>The Innovators</b></a>&nbsp;</span><b>★★★★★</b></li><li><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1165336021" target="_blank"><b>Zero to One</b></a>&nbsp;</span><b>★★★★★</b></li></ul></div><div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><br />I have to admit that I gave up on <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1165337209" target="_blank"><b>Capital in the Twenty-First Century</b></a> and gave it&nbsp;</span><b>★★</b><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;">.</span></